## WireGuard Tunnel (VPS ↔ CasaOS)

| Side | WireGuard IP |
|------|-------------|
| VPS | `10.10.10.1` |
| CasaOS | `10.10.10.2` |

**OPNsense rules — explicit allowlist (default-deny):**

| Proto | Dest | Port | Service |
|-------|------|------|---------|
| TCP | CasaOS | 80 | CasaOS web / nginx |
| TCP | CasaOS | 9010 | Authentik |

> Every other CasaOS service port is **blocked**. To expose a new service: `OPNsense → Interfaces → WireGuard → Firewall Rules → Add`.
> After reboot a pass rule is required — default policy is deny.
> **FreeBSD/csh limitation on OPNsense**: multi-line SSH one-liners don't work — use single-line commands only.

