## Critical Gotchas

1. **VPS fail2ban**: One failed SSH login bans `108.53.225.137` (home IP) on all ports. Use Racknerd VNC console if locked out. Unban: `fail2ban-client set sshd unbanip 108.53.225.137`
2. **VPS SSH key**: Must use `id_rsa`, NOT `id_ed25519` — ed25519 is rejected
3. **Jellyfin + Authentik**: Forward auth on `jellyfin.streamy.tube` breaks API clients (CORS errors). Apps must use `http://192.168.50.19:8096` directly
4. **Port 5432 reserved**: mem0-postgres (Sadie/FamilyHub) owns it — any new Postgres must use a different port
5. **WireGuard default-deny**: After OPNsense reboot, verify pass rules are active — new ports silently fail without explicit rules
6. **Ollama is NOT on CasaOS**: It runs on the separate ollama-vm at `192.168.50.62` (LAN) or `100.70.195.84` (Tailscale)
7. **OPNsense shell**: Uses FreeBSD csh — multi-line SSH heredocs don't work, use single-line commands
8. **ubuntu-claude repo path**: `~/Dev/BrickLayer2.0` with capital B and L (not `Bricklayer2.0` like WSL)
